product.title: Misty mountains with Blushing Cherry Blossom Tee
product.body_html:
• Description
  • FAQ
  • Shipping

  • Bring nature to life with its beautiful depiction of misty mountains and blushing sakura petals  

    This tee is a stunning piece of art that captures the beauty and mystery of nature. The front features a wild skaura, a rare and exotic flower that blooms only once a year, in contrast with the misty mountains in the background.

    This tee is perfect for anyone who loves adventure, romance, and elegance. It will make you feel like you are part of a fairy tale every time you wear it.

    Available in 12 colors and 7 different sizes, measurements are shown below. We always recommend choosing 1-2 sizes larger and comparing the measurements in the sizing chart to a tee that fits you.

    Size (inches) XS S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 34 36 38 41 43 45 47
    Length  25 26 27 28 28 29 30
                   
    Size (cm) XS S M L XL XXL XXXL
    Bust 88 92 98 104 110 115 120
    Length     64 66 68 71 73 75 77

    If you are interested in more items like this, please check out our website www.kawaiies.com.

    Features

    🍙 Made with Modal and 100% Cotton
    🍙 Short oversized sleeves
    🍙 Three different designs printed on the front


    Measurements may be off by 1-5cm for rounding up to a whole number.

  • Please follow the washing labels when cleaning the garment:

     Max temperature 30c, or cold water. Reverse garment to protect the print.

     Do not bleach

     Dry by the sun or hang it to dry. 

     Dry cleaning

     

  • FREE Tracked Shipping to the United States, Canada, United Kingdom, Australia, New Zealand, Germany, Spain, France, Italy, Austria, Netherlands, and many more. Find out more here: Shipping Policy.

    Packaging time: 1-3 Business days

    Shipping time: Est 5-30 Business days
